<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.1. SLIP 4"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-1a.1">君子之於教也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-1a.2">其導民也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-1a.3">不浸，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-1a.4">則其淳也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-1a.5">弗深矣.</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.2. SLIPS 4-6"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-2a.1">是故亡乎其身</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-2a.2">而 存乎其詞，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-2a.3">雖厚其令，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-2a.4">民弗從之矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-2a.5">是故威服刑罰之屢行也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-2a.6">由上之弗身也。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.3. SLIPS 6-7"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-3a.1">昔者君子有言曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-3a.2">戰與刑，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-3a.3">人君子之墜德也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-3a.4">是故上苟身服之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-3a.5">則民必有甚焉者。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.4. SLIPS 7-9"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-4a.1">君袀冕</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-4a.2">而立於阼，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-4a.3">一宮之人不勝其敬。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-4a.4">君衰絰而處位，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-4a.5">一宮之人不勝其 [哀];</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-4a.6">[君冠冑帶甲而立於軍],</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.5. SLIPS 9-10"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.1">上苟倡之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.2">則民鮮不從矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.3">雖然，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.4">其存也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.5">不厚，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.6">其重也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.7">弗多矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.8">是故君子之求諸己也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-5a.9">深。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.6. SLIPS 10-12"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.1">不求諸其本而攻諸其末，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.2">弗得矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.3">是故君子之於言也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.4">非從末流者之貴，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.5">窮源反本者之貴。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.6">苟不從其由，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.7">不反其本，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-6a.8">未有可得也者。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.7. SLIPS 12-13"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-7a.1">君上享成不唯本，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-7a.2">功〔弗就矣〕。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-7a.3">農夫務食不強耕，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-7a.4">糧弗足矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-7a.5">士成言不行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-7a.6">名弗得矣。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.8. SLIPS 13-15"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-8a.1">是故君子之於言也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-8a.2">非從末流者之貴，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-8a.3">窮源反本者之貴。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-8a.4">苟不從其由，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-8a.5">不反其本，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-8a.6">雖強之弗入矣。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.9. SLIPS 15-17"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.1">上不以其道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.2">民之從之也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.3">難。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.4">是以民可敬導也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.5">而不可掩（=抑）也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.6">可御也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.7">而不可牽也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.8">故君子不貴庶物，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-9a.9">而貴與民有同也。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.10. SLIPS 17-19"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.1">智而比次，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.2">則民欲其智之遂也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.3">富而分賤，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.4">則民欲其富之大也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.5">貴而能讓，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.6">則民欲其貴之上也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.7">反此道也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.8">民必因此重也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.9">以報之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-10a.10">可不慎乎？</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.11. SLIPS 19-20"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.1">故君子所報之不多，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.2">所求之不遠，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.3">察反諸己</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.4">而可以知人.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.5">是故欲人之愛己也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.6">則必先愛人；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.7">欲人之敬己也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-11a.8">則必先敬人。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.12. SLIPS 31-33"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a.1">天降大常，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a.2">以理人倫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a.3">制為君臣之義，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a.4">著為父子之親，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a.5">分為夫婦之辨。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a.6">是故小人亂天常以逆大道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-12a.7">君子治人倫以順天德。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.13. SLIPS 33-34"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.1">大禹曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.2">「余茲度 (宅GDE)天心」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.3">何？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.4">此言也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.5">舍之此而度(宅GDE)於天心也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.6">是故君子簟席之上，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.7">讓而授幼；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.8">朝廷之位，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.9">讓而處賤；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-13a.10">所度(宅GDE)不遠矣。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.14. SLIPS 34-36"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a" ed="tls" n="001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.1">小人不逞人於忍，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.2">君子不逞人於禮。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.3">津梁爭舟，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.4">其先也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.5">不若其後也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.6">言語較之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.7">其勝也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.8">不若其已也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.9">君子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.10">從允釋過，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.11">則先者除，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-14a.12">來者信。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.15. SLIPS 29-30+1"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a" ed="tls" n="001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.1">《君奭》曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.2">「襄我二人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.3">毋有合在音」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.4">何？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.5">道不悅之詞也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.6">君子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.7">雖有其恒而可,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.8">能終之為難。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.9">槁木三年，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.10">不必為封旗。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.11">何？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.12">言</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.13">陳[挾=達DYZ]之也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-15a.14">是以君子貴成之。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.16. SLIPS 1-3"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a" ed="tls" n="001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.1">聞之曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.2">古之用民者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.3">求之於己為恒。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.4">行不信則命不從，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.5">信不著則言不樂。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.6">民不從上之命，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.7">不信其言，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.8">而能含德者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-16a.9">未之有也。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.17. SLIPS 3+24-25"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a" ed="tls" n="001-17a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.1">故君子之蒞民也，Therefore if the gentleman facing (towards) the people,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.2">身服善以先之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.3">敬慎以守之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.4">其所存者入矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.5">民孰弗從？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.6">形於中，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.7">發於色，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.8">其蕩(睟DYZ)也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.9">固矣;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.10">民孰弗信?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.11">是以上之恒務，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-17a.12">在信於眾。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.18. SLIP 25"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a" ed="tls" n="001-18a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a.1">《詔命》曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a.2">「允師濟德。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a.3">何？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a.4">此言也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a.5">言</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a.6">信於眾之[時MC]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-18a.7">可以濟德也。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.19. SLIPS 25-27"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a" ed="tls" n="001-19a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a.1">聖人之性與中人之性，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a.2">其生而未有非[別DYZ]之。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a.3">節於儒[而GDE (=此)DYZ]也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a.4">則猶是也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a.5">雖其於善道也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a.6">亦非有擇,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-19a.7">數以多也 (?);</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.20. SLIPS 27-28+22"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-20a" ed="tls" n="001-20a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-20a.1">及其博長而厚大也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-20a.2">則聖人不可猶豫憚之。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-20a.3">此以民皆有性</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-20a.4">而聖人不可慕也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-20a.5">是故凡物在疾之。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.21. SLIPS 22-23"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a" ed="tls" n="001-21a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.1">《君奭》曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.2">「惟冒丕單稱德」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.3">何？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.4">言疾也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.5">君子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.6">疾之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.7">行之不疾，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-21a.8">未有能深之者也。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.22. SLIPS 23+21"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a" ed="tls" n="001-22a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.1">勉之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.2">遂也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.3">強之工也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.4">陳之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.5">淹也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.6">辭之工也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.7">是以智</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.8">而求之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.9">不疾，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.10">其去人</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.11">弗遠矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.12">勇而行之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.13">不果</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.14">其疑也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-22a.15">弗往(匡MC)矣。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.23. SLIPS 37-38"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a" ed="tls" n="001-23a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a.1">唯君子道可近求，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a.2">而可遠措也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a.3">昔者君子有言曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a.4">「聖人天德」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a.5">何？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a.6">言慎求之於己，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-23a.7">而可以至順天常矣。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN CHENGZHIWENZHI 11.24. SLIPS 38-40"><pb xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a" ed="tls" n="001-24a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.1">《康誥》曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.2">「不還大戛，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.3">文王作罰，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.4">刑茲亡赦」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.5">何？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.6">此言也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.7">言</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.8">不逆大常者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.9">文王之刑莫重焉。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.10">是 故君子慎六位</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0024_tls_001-24a.11">以祀天常。</seg></p>

